---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Driveway Installation',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Driveway installation across East Texas — concrete, asphalt, and gravel driveways with proper base preparation, drainage grading, and culvert installation for East Texas properties.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Driveway Installation East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Driveway installation across East Texas — concrete, asphalt, and gravel with proper base prep and drainage grading. Purpose Construction serves East Texas properties. Call (936) 555-5555."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Outdoor Living', href: '/outdoor-living' }, { label: 'Driveway Installation', href: '/driveway-installation' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Driveway Installation in East Texas" subtitle="Concrete, asphalt, and gravel driveways built with proper base preparation, drainage grading, and culvert installation for East Texas properties." tag="Outdoor Living Service" 
    image="/images/driveway-installation-east-texas.jpg"
  />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Driveway Installation" title="Driveways That Hold Up Through East Texas Rain Seasons" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>A driveway is only as good as the base underneath it and the drainage designed around it. East Texas clay soils shift with moisture — without a properly compacted base, even a well-poured concrete driveway will crack and heave within a few years. Purpose Construction prepares subgrade correctly, brings in proper base material, and grades for drainage before any surface material is placed, whether that's concrete, asphalt, or gravel.</p>
            <p>For rural properties along county roads and FM routes in Angelina County, culvert installation is often required at the road connection to keep your driveway from washing out and blocking county drainage. We handle culvert sizing and installation as part of the driveway project so the whole system works together. Concrete driveways are particularly popular in Lufkin for their longevity and low maintenance — we add expansion joints and proper edge detailing to minimize cracking over time.</p>
            <p>We also install gravel driveways for rural properties and long drives where concrete isn't practical, using proper base preparation and appropriate gravel materials for East Texas conditions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
            <a href="/outdoor-living" class="btn-outline">All Outdoor Living</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/driveway-installation-east-texas.jpg" alt="Driveway installation across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Driveway Installation Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['Concrete Driveway', 'Asphalt', 'Gravel', 'Base Preparation', 'Drainage Grading', 'Expansion Joints', 'Sealing', 'Culvert Installation'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Outdoor Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Walkway Installation', href: '/walkway-installation' }, { label: 'Fence Installation', href: '/fence-installation' }, { label: 'Outdoor Living', href: '/outdoor-living' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Ready for a New Driveway?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction for a free driveway estimate. We serve Lufkin and all of East Texas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
